{"tid":1633920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一齊帶小丑面具上街","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T15:11:28.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"48f54a79996b7bfbe5d9dc5533a425bdd064c925","tid":1633920,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d07e3e391971cee9a79c702a173c0512956d17d","tid":1633920,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:39.000Z","msg":"罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但和勇合一係成場運動既關鍵，兩樣一齊做唔撚得？講緊既係，拆鐵係唔撚會影響人權法，或所謂既民意，但對政權、運動係現時有最大既影響力"},{"pid":"5bebad35a0f0687f45a32e579fe6232afd8bbce7","tid":1633920,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:49:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好醜化自己 兩件事都喺社會逼成 但本質唔同</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3deccb8dae3058cfd82051c19e006a04601425d5","tid":1633920,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bebad35a0f0687f45a32e579fe6232afd8bbce7","tid":1633920,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:49:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好醜化自己 兩件事都喺社會逼成 但本質唔同